{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"727","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"資本額150億元公司 7月起須發布英文重訊","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-06-30 16:12 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>經濟日報<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>記者趙于萱<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>即時報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80.JPG' style='width: 800px; height: 597px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>證交所表示，為加速台灣資本市場雙語化並提升金融競爭力，明（<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>）日起，凡<span lang='EN-US'>108</span>年底實收資本額達<span lang='EN-US'>150</span>億元以上的上市公司，發布重大訊息均須中、英文同步發布。圖／聯合報系資料照片</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>證交所表示，為加速台灣資本市場雙語化並提升金融競爭力，明（<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>）日起，凡<span lang='EN-US'>108</span>年底實收資本額達<span lang='EN-US'>150</span>億元以上的上市公司，發布重大訊息均須中、英文同步發布；提醒上市公司及早因應，以利及時發送重大訊息。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>證交所今年初修正「對有價證券上市公司重大訊息之查證暨公開處理程序」部分條文，分四階段實施上市公司重大訊息「雙語化」，第一階段將於<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>日起上路，也就是明天開始，資本額達標準的上市公司均須齊步發布英文重大訊息。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經統計，第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>階段適用公司有<span lang='EN-US'>86</span>家，加上目前已發布英文重大訊息的上市公司，共計<span lang='EN-US'>343</span>家，達整體上市公司的<span lang='EN-US'>36%</span>，市值涵蓋全體上市公司則達到<span lang='EN-US'>85%</span>。有利外資即時掌握企業資訊，提升我國資本市場國際化。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>證交所指出，第二階段雙語化規劃明（<span lang='EN-US'>110</span>）年起生效，除前述已適用公司，持續遵循雙語規範，<span lang='EN-US'>109</span>年底實收資本額達<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>億元以上、或<span lang='EN-US'>109</span>年度召開股東常會股東名簿記載之外資及陸資持股比率合計<span lang='EN-US'>30%</span>之上市公司，也將適用。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>第三階段則自後（<span lang='EN-US'>111</span>）年生效，加入<span lang='EN-US'>110</span>年底及<span lang='EN-US'>111</span>年底實收資本額達<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>億元以上、或<span lang='EN-US'>110</span>年及<span lang='EN-US'>111</span>年召開股東常會時股東名簿記載之外資及陸資持股比率合計達<span lang='EN-US'>30%</span>以上者。於次年起，即分別於<span lang='EN-US'>111</span>年及<span lang='EN-US'>112</span>年適用發布英文重大訊息。第四階段自<span lang='EN-US'>113</span>年生效，全體上市公司都適用發布英文重訊。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/7251/4668989</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-07-02","clk_count":"213"}},"__N_SSG":true}